{"tid":1275331,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論戰重要武器：台灣太陽花佔領判詞","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T01:23:47.000Z","uid":4610,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"265e56cd7aaec2782fc9d2f1ba7092d207ccc85e","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F91460&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=d7b01bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91460</a><br />\n太陽花佔領立院二審再判無罪，因<span style=\"color: red;\">「屬最後必要手段」</span><br />\n合議庭宣判時表示，二審並未援引「公民不服從」概念，但認為太陽花學運肇因於反服貿黑箱，民眾陳抗並未主動攻擊警方，過程中<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾或有與員警推擠衝撞</span>，但沒有人持器械攻擊，也沒有<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重流血衝突</span>，檢方上訴指控黃國昌等人涉犯煽惑他人犯罪沒有理由，駁回上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有暴徒 只有暴政</span></span>"},{"pid":"2164b51947daa35c8c242668fb649a81f6b0a551","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"22a67a0d3ad9ecaa8102cbaa5e92903f71970c2c","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:27.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"d460041207109cf19b30a85fc44ab7f77d399b26","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"737adc11a8d82a7bad795291131840ac25a41bc1","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:51.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a4c7139d170923ae027bb8f69384a8cb7f4a4b73","tid":1275331,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0229aac9f0036cebfeabf1e8832e9c49eb4e5d71","tid":1275331,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim